==English==

===Noun===
'''[[lip]] [[service]]'''
#{{idiom}} Empty [[talk]]; [[words]] [[absent]] of [[action]] or [[intention]].
#:''The candidate gave '''lip service''' to fixing the problems, but it is doubtful that he will do much.''
#Another term (emerging out of [[queer]] culture) that describes [[cunnilingus]], the act of using the [[mouth]] and [[tongue]] to stimulate the female genitals, especially the [[clitoris]] and [[labium]]. Sometimes also referred to as '''giving lip'''.
#:''Michio gave Suzume '''lip service'''.''